The SIAM market is segmented based on components, organization size, verticals, deployment modes, and geographical regions. The solutions and services segment provides a comprehensive range of offerings to cater to the diverse needs of organizations. Large enterprises and small to medium enterprises have specific requirements when it comes to managing service integrations and providers. Various verticals such as IT, BFSI, retail, healthcare, and government sectors are increasingly adopting SIAM for efficient service management. The deployment mode options of on-premises and cloud offer flexibility to organizations based on their IT infrastructure preferences. Geographically, North America is a significant market for SIAM due to the high adoption of advanced IT services, followed by Europe, Asia-Pacific, the Middle East, and Africa, and Latin America.

